//www.taiwanthinktank.org/page/chinese_attachment_1/1752/012_20100910.pdf |format=PDF |title=2010 美國國防部「中國軍力報告書」研析 |language=中文 |publisher=台灣智庫 |date=2010-09-10 |accessdate=2016-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108195058/http://www.taiwanthinktank.org/page/chinese_attachment_1/1752/012_20100910.pdf |archive-date=2016-11-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="US2012">{{cite book |url=http://www.defense.gov/Portals/1/Documents/pubs/2012_CMPR_Final.pdf |format=PDF |title=Military and Security Developments Involving the People’s Republic of China 2012 |publisher=Office of the Secretary of Defense |date=2012 |accessdate=2016-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221110156/http://www.defense.gov/Portals/1/Documents/pubs/2012_CMPR_Final.pdf |archive-date=2016-12-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="US2016">{{cite book |url=http://www.defense.gov/Portals/1/Documents/pubs/2016%20China%20Military%20Power%20Report.pdf |format=PDF |title=Military and Security Developments Involving the People’s Republic of China 2016 |publisher=Office of the Secretary of Defense |date=2016-04-26 |accessdate=2016-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104135047/http://www.defense.gov/Portals/1/Documents/pubs/2016%20China%20Military%20Power%20Report.pdf |archive-date=2016-11-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。自1996年台海危机后，台湾就决定发展[[中程导弹|中程导弹]]。1999年，前国民党投管会主委[[劉泰英|刘泰英]]说台湾的飞弹也可打到[[香港|香港]]、[[上海|上海]]。2004年5月，美国国防部提出[[台军攻击三峡大坝论|台军攻击三峡大坝论]]。6月，国防部副部长[[蔡明憲|蔡明宪]]承认台湾有能力攻击[[三峡大坝|三峡大坝]]。9月，时任行政院院长的[[游锡堃|游锡堃]]认为台湾要保持足够反制力，在立法院备询时提出「你打我100顆，我就打你50顆，你打我台北、高雄，我就打你上海。」的[[恐怖平衡|恐怖平衡]]观点。媒体报道指，[[李登輝政府|李登辉]]、[[陈水扁政府|陈水扁]]、[[马英九政府|马英九]]三任政府皆积极推进中程导弹研发计划——[[雲峰飛彈|云峰计划]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6773/2931606 |title=「打三峽大壩沒人性」 但老美也曾建議我們炸下去 |accessdate=2020-07-30 |author=黃國樑 |date=2018-01-16 |work= |publisher=联合新闻网 |language=Zh-hant |archive-date=2020-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712063124/https://theme.udn.com/theme/story/6773/2931606 |de